自己未來擔憂，令我更下定決心，盡一己之力為青年奮鬥！青年人！站起來！爭取民主！爭取自由！」而她以「李詩詠 Wing」作下款。<br />\n而Ceci的選舉廣告及材料相當「平民」，與一般的候選人明顯有別。幸好，經過多番努力，她在前日（7日）終於有自己的選舉宣傳品，她急不及待放上facebook與網民分享，又不忘加tag「#香港人，加油！」、「#青年人，站起來！」。<br />\n雖然Ceci積極走親民路線，不過，她在facebook曾出post表示：「這個過程雖困難，而目（且）不停被對手攻擊誣衊。我會努力站起來。」有不少網民表示支持，而且還問她會否擺街站，但有網民留言稱：「忙到連字都唔識打仲點相信你可以服務社區啊？」Ceci親自回覆說：「那麼，你可以相信保皇黨。 香港人，加油！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191109/60249835\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191109%2F60249835&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGAexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=835c8c6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191109%2F60249835&h=3a808a62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191109/60249835</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/cecillliii/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcecillliii%2F&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGAexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=50d9bd3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/cecillliii/</a><br />\n佢個fb好似唔見左,ig又唔見佢post選舉d野,唔知佢選黎為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba46c73769dbb62efdbdcf3b5e57c23292e95331","tid":1695153,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f1cf672a295911de611668add3a200cc7e6be23","tid":1695153,"uid":240608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:02:33.000Z","msg":"2個肥仔好似樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但副眼鏡唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}